cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

The paper focuses on natural language grounded navigation in photo-realistic environments, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a multitask learning approach and environment-agnostic representations, which are related to artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with navigation in physical environments, which is related to robotics (RO) sub-category.
